      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## EDA: Feature Distributions (Outlier Evidence)\n",
        "\n",
        "We plot feature distributions to observe skew and potential extreme values.\n",
        "Because some features can contain outliers/skewness, we adopt **RobustScaler**\n",
        "for scale-sensitive models (e.g., Logistic Regression).\n",
        "RobustScaler uses median and IQR, which is less sensitive to outliers than StandardScaler."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "u3wS_TJwRUhV"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "df.drop(columns=[\"quality_label\"]).hist(bins=20, figsize=(14, 10))\n",
        "plt.suptitle(\"Feature Distributions (Red Wine)\")\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 930
        },
        "id": "DbpbpmErQdP-",
        "outputId": "a772156e-81fb-4d0a-ce78-2eddef84cf87"
